description: Set in the heart of South Boston, this home stands out with stylish updates and thoughtful details. Renovated in 2010, this parlor level unit features hardwood floors, custom built-ins, designer lighting, and a charming window seat overlooking the vibrant energy of East Broadway. The open floor plan and soaring 10-foot ceilings create a bright, spacious feel, while central air and a living room wired for surround sound make entertaining effortless. A shared patio offers additional space for gatherings or relaxation. The kitchen is beautifully appointed with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a modern backsplash, and the convenience of a dishwasher and disposal. With free common laundry and abundant storage, this home checks all the boxes for comfortable city living. Unit is currently tenanted month to month, making it perfect for an investor or owner occupant.
